{"tid":2095332,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"得罪講句，鐵血嘅魔劍等於seed嘅核彈","createTime":"2020-07-05T11:10:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T17:32:25.000Z","uid":57911,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e800559073f5871019dbabf688a4b3aaf93d83d5","tid":2095332,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:10:34.000Z","msg":"睇設定就會知，魔劍係禁忌嘅科技，同核彈係同一種限制<br />\n<br />\n我哋正常人眼見把魔劍只係把普通實體兵器，實際出嚟效果一定係有追蹤功能嘅超科技喺入面<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係你都解釋唔到點解魔劍會同核彈有同一種待遇<br />\n<br />\n見seed咁多人討論，唔差在幫魔劍平反埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a286e859cf96b2f8d1f9b2d722a050d8135ad978","tid":2095332,"uid":155818,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:12:07.000Z","msg":"唔好再講呢套垃圾<br />\n睇見魔劍都想嘔"},{"pid":"cbb7e3da5e983482e46415e26704144706a8073f","tid":2095332,"uid":156913,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:12:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WLxJJZc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FWLxJJZc.gif&h=b0056a75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64a7760951a8fbf4ab8e5b00bae0d99faa19e0dc","tid":2095332,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:17:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好再講呢套垃圾<br />\n睇見魔劍都想嘔</blockquote><br />\n大家誤解咗個超前科技，一定要以正視聽"},{"pid":"512bceaf58358dba7fafc608a16b6533a037bdec","tid":2095332,"uid":8307,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:18:32.000Z","msg":"鐵血應該改魔劍做質量炮,咁樣個演出就好睇好多<br />\n同埋個精確度都合理好多"},{"pid":"1fcd3168c22e1fb969fd71605747d6911f0d23aa","tid":2095332,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:20:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鐵血應該改魔劍做質量炮,咁樣個演出就好睇好多<br />\n同埋個精確度都合理好多</blockquote><br />\n依個真，做設計嗰個傻鳩嚟，seed都識整創世大砲，G復興都識整納米爆彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85add909db3bbfa1b2933a280a6d50b357f86e0","tid":2095332,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dis